<section class="bg-gunmetal py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl" data-animate>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-off-white sm:text-4xl">
        Built for the AI Era
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-off-white/70 leading-relaxed">
        Fierro ships with a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server. That means your AI
        tools don't just sit next to your project data -- they read it directly.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-off-white/10 bg-off-white/5 p-6" data-animate>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-off-white">Works with ChatGPT</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-off-white/70">
            Have ChatGPT draft a cost report from your expense data. Ask it to
            flag budget items trending over estimate. Your data, your prompts,
            real answers.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-off-white/10 bg-off-white/5 p-6" data-animate>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-off-white">Works with Claude</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-off-white/70">
            Ask Claude to summarize your project budget. Have it compare
            actuals against estimates across all your sub-projects. No copy-paste,
            no CSV exports -- just direct access.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 rounded-lg border border-off-white/10 bg-off-white/5 p-6" data-animate>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-off-white">Tiered AI Access</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-off-white/70">
          The Free tier includes limited AI access so you can see it in action.
          Plus and Builder tiers get fully configurable AI/MCP integration -- connect
          your preferred AI tools and customize how they interact with your project data.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
